{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">1.知道酸或碱能使指示剂变色；</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">2.掌握酚酞和石蕊在不同酸碱性下的颜色。</span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">在酸性条件下石蕊为红色，中性为紫色，碱性为蓝色；在酸性和中性条件下酚酞为无色，碱性为红色。</span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">仪器：胶头滴管、点滴板。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">药品：氢氧化钠溶液、氢氧化钙溶液、稀盐酸、稀硫酸、酚酞、石蕊。</span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">在点滴板的四个孔中分别滴加2ml氢氧化钠溶液、氢氧化钙溶液、稀盐酸和稀硫酸，然后分别滴加酚酞，观察实验现象。在另一个点滴板中的四个孔中分别滴加2ml氢氧化钠溶液、氢氧化钙溶液、稀盐酸和稀硫酸，然后分别滴加石蕊，观察实验现象。</span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<table border=\"1\" style=\"width:700px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">溶液</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">加入石蕊后的颜色</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">加入酚酞后的颜色</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">氢氧化钙溶液</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">蓝色</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">红色</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">氢氧化钠溶液</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">蓝色</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">红色</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">稀盐酸</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">红色</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">无色</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">稀硫酸</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">红色</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">无色</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}